OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency received more
OL,7,Fthan 250 odour complaints last month
OL,8,Fabout a smell that has been plaguing
OL,9,Fresidents in a Cumbrian town for
OL,10,Fdecades.
OL,12,FA Freedom of Information request by
OL,13,Fcampaigners showed that there were 277
OL,14,Fregarding the so-called 'Penrith Pong'
OL,15,Fin June, compared to 67 in May.
OL,17,FNow the local campaigners and the MP
OL,18,Ffor Penrith and Solway, Markus
OL,19,FCampbell-Savours, say they are
OL,20,Fdetermined to find out what is causing
OL,21,Fit.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
