FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783956016
OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,FJeff Thomson of the Fresh AIR for
OL,7,FPenrith Campaign is telling the
OL,8,Fauthorities "to put an end to it".
OL,10,FPeople have previously blamed Omega
OL,11,FProteins, the animal rendering plant
OL,12,Fwhich processes abattoir waste into
OL,13,Fmeat on the outskirts of the town.
OL,15,FThe factory's owners, the Leo Group,
OL,16,Fsay they have spent more than #100m in
OL,17,Fthe past ten years or so on odour
OL,18,Fcontrol technology.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
