FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783956016
OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,FBosses added there were "various
OL,7,Fsources" for the odours and it had
OL,8,Finstalled "multiple odour abatement
OL,9,Ftechnologies" at its site.
OL,11,FThe Environment Agency says it
OL,12,Fregularly monitors the plant.
OL,14,FMarkus CampbellSavours chaired a
OL,15,Fsecond meeting between the Environment
OL,16,FAgency and Penrith Town Council
OL,17,Frecently to address ongoing odour
OL,18,Fconcerns affecting residents and
OL,19,Fbusinesses across the town.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783956016
OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,FThe potential causes of the odour were
OL,7,Fdiscussed, as well as its reported
OL,8,Fimpacts on physical and mental
OL,9,Fwellbeing, and the Environment
OL,10,FAgency's permitting arrangements.
OL,12,FMarkus CampbellSavours MP said: "I
OL,13,Fwas contacted by Penrith Town Council
OL,14,Fregarding air quality and odour issues
OL,15,Fin Penrith and expressing their
OL,16,Fconcerns that the Environment Agency
OL,17,Fhad declined to meet with them.
OL,26,@tD@bOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783956016
OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,F"Whilst I recognise Penrith Town
OL,7,FCouncil has a limited role in these
OL,8,Fmatters, they are elected members just
OL,9,Flike myself, and the community expects
OL,10,Fus to challenge those responsible to
OL,11,Fprevent this disgusting smell.
OL,13,F"I am pleased that Jeff Thomson from
OL,14,FFresh Air for Penrith was in
OL,15,Fattendance and I support his drive to
OL,16,Fsee Penrith residents raise their
OL,17,Fconcerns with the Environment Agency
OL,18,Fon the days when the problem presents
OL,19,Fitself.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783956016
OL,3,C'Put an end to it', say campaigners on
OL,4,CPenrith factory odour complaints
OL,6,F"It's only through creating this
OL,7,Fevidence base that we can ensure
OL,8,Fregulators like the Environment Agency
OL,9,Fwill take responsibility.
OL,11,F"In the days following our meeting and
OL,12,Fwith this unusually hot weather, my
OL,13,Finbox is bulging with residents
OL,14,Fexpressing concerns.
OL,16,F"My message to those responsible is
OL,17,Fwork with the community, accept there
OL,18,Fis a problem and fix it once and for
OL,19,Fall."
OL,26,@{D@EO]
